(107, 'Who''s Online', '', '', 9, 'sidebar-a', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 1, 'mod_whosonline', 1, 1, '{"showmode":"0","layout":"_:default","moduleclass_sfx":"hidden-phone","cache":"0","filter_groups":"0"}', 0, '*'),
(109, 'Title4 Module Variation', '', '<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua.</p>\r\n\r\n<a href="#" class="readon">Button</a>', 2, 'content-bottom-b', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 1, 'mod_custom', 1, 1, '{"prepare_content":"1","backgroundimage":"","layout":"_:default","moduleclass_sfx":"title4","cache":"1","cache_time":"900","cachemode":"static"}', 0, '*'),
(110, 'Login Form', '', '', 6, 'sidebar-a', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 1, 'mod_login', 1, 1, '{"pretext":"","posttext":"","login":"","logout":"","greeting":"1","name":"0","usesecure":"0","layout":"_:default","moduleclass_sfx":"hidden-tablet hidden-phone","cache":"0"}', 0, '*'),
(111, 'Collapsible Positions', '', '<p>If no modules are published to a position, the entire area or row will not appear or collapse.</p>', 14, 'sidebar-a', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 1, 'mod_custom', 1, 1, '{"prepare_content":"1","backgroundimage":"","layout":"_:default","moduleclass_sfx":"box2","cache":"1","cache_time":"900","cachemode":"static"}', 0, '*'),
(112, 'Injected Features', '', '<p><strong>Features</strong> are specific elements of functionality, that are incredibly flexible and can be used to perform any kind of logic you would need. They are injected into a <strong>position</strong> when enabled, and are stacked vertically; inclusive of: Date, <strong>Font Sizer</strong>, Login Panel and more.</p>', 12, 'sidebar-a', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 1, 'mod_custom', 1, 1, '{"prepare_content":"1","backgroundimage":"","layout":"_:default","moduleclass_sfx":"box1","cache":"1","cache_time":"900","cachemode":"static"}', 0, '*'),
(113, 'Grid Sizes', '', '<p>Configure at <strong>Admin → Extensions → Template Manager → rt_graffito</strong>, then go to <strong>Layouts</strong> to set the grid widths and allocated positions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>By default, each grid is given an <strong>equal</strong> distribution, but this can be modified to a <strong>custom</strong> distribution between modules, such as <strong>3/4/5</strong> instead of <strong>4/4/4</strong>. These options are available for when <strong>2-6</strong> modules are present.</p>', 13, 'sidebar-a', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 1, 'mod_custom', 1, 1, '{"prepare_content":"1","backgroundimage":"","layout":"_:default","moduleclass_sfx":"","cache":"1","cache_time":"900","cachemode":"static"}', 0, '*'),
(114, 'Forced Positions', '', '<p>There are times when you just don''t want to have your modules taking up all the room in a horizontal row no matter what the layout. For example you might want to have a module on the left and a module on the right, with nothing in the middle.</p> \r\n\r\n<p>This is made easy with Gantry with the <strong>Force Positions</strong> parameter for each layout, allowing you to set the <strong>count</strong> to a specific row number, such as 4, even if 4 modules are not published for that row.</p>', 11, 'sidebar-a', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 1, 'mod_custom', 1, 1, '{"prepare_content":"1","backgroundimage":"","layout":"_:default","moduleclass_sfx":"","cache":"1","cache_time":"900","cachemode":"static"}', 0, '*'),
(115, 'MainBody Layouts', '', '<p>Configure at <strong>Admin → Extensions → Template Manager → rt_gantry</strong>, then go to <strong>Layouts</strong> tab and set the varying Mainbody/Sidebar layout possibilities.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Here, you can change both the grid size of the <strong>Mainbody/Sidebar</strong> position, but also the location of the sidebars. You can place the sidebars at varying <strong>combinations</strong> to the left, right or both or the Mainbody.</p>', 10, 'sidebar-a', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 1, 'mod_custom', 1, 1, '{"prepare_content":"1","backgroundimage":"","layout":"_:default","moduleclass_sfx":"box2","cache":"1","cache_time":"900","cachemode":"static"}', 0, '*'),
(116, 'Menu Module', '', '<p>This is an example of a module being displayed inside the menu <strong>dropdowns</strong>.</p>\r\n<p><a href="#" class="readon"><span>Read More</span></a></p>', 0, 'menu-mod', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 1, 'mod_custom', 1, 0, '{"prepare_content":"1","backgroundimage":"","layout":"_:default","moduleclass_sfx":"","cache":"1","cache_time":"900","cachemode":"static"}', 0, '*'),
(117, 'Help & Guides', '', '<p class="hidden-large">A rich resource of Video and Written tutorials are available at Gantry-Framework.org.</p>\r\n<p class="visible-large">A rich resource of Video and Written tutorials are available.</p>\r\n<p><a class="readon" href="http://www.gantry-framework.org/">Read More</a></p>', 8, 'sidebar-a', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 1, 'mod_custom', 1, 1, '{"prepare_content":"1","backgroundimage":"","layout":"_:default","moduleclass_sfx":"nomargintop nopaddingtop","cache":"1","cache_time":"900","cachemode":"static"}', 0, '*');

